      "content": "the helpline thing is just... it's just words. they don't get it. they don't know how it feels for the person who is left behind. it's not just being sad, it's like the actual air has left the room. i feel like a shell of a person. what's the point of \"reaching out\" when the person i actually need to talk to is gone forever? everything is just empty.",
